init_text:
A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She’s unaware that she’s actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who’s fallen for her, and is certain he’s going to get it right this time.

One day,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She had never seen one before, and was shocked at the size of it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The man was bleeding badly, and she didn't know what to do.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I have to get you to a hospital" she said.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She pulled out her cell phone and dialed 911.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm on the mountain trail, near the old mill" she said.
